text: Ani samudrannahi tumacya adhina karuna thevale ahe ki tumhi yatuna nighalele taje mansa khave ani yatuna apalya angavara ghalanyakarita dagine kadhu sakave, ani tumhi pahala ki nava yata panyala cirata calatata ani yasathihi ki tumhi tyacya krpeca sodha ghyava ani sambhavatah tumhi krtajnatahi vyakta karavi
